        <title type="html"><![CDATA[【2024最新可用】操作简单安全的美区AppleID礼品卡购买教程]]></title>
        <id>https://blog.393837.xyz/post/Apple-ID/</id>
        <link href="https://blog.393837.xyz/post/Apple-ID/">
        </link>
        <updated>2024-02-17T11:16:59.000Z</updated>
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<blockquote>
<p>封面图来自<a href="https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/636121931">【2023年最新】操作简单又安全靠谱的美区AppleID礼品卡购买充值保姆级教程 - 知乎</a></p>
</blockquote>
<h1 id="这篇内容教大家在支付宝购买-app-store-美区礼品卡">这篇内容教大家在支付宝购买 App Store 美区礼品卡</h1>
<p><strong>操作简单、安全、无中间商赚差价！</strong><br>
这里是Region，我通过这个方法为美区 Apple ID 充钱，目前没有什么问题。<br>
话不多说，教程开始，只要跟着我的步骤走百分百都能成功（<strong>先看完文章再操作</strong>）</p>
<h2 id="一-支付宝购买">一、支付宝购买</h2>
<p>1、打开<strong>支付宝</strong>APP<br>
<img src="https://krseoul.imgtbl.com/i/2024/02/17/65d09ae755b8d.jpg" alt="IMG_4293.jpg" loading="lazy"><br>
2、搜索<strong>Pockyt Shop</strong>并打开<br>
<img src="https://krseoul.imgtbl.com/i/2024/02/17/65d09ae560998.png" alt="IMG_4294.PNG" loading="lazy"><br>
<img src="https://krseoul.imgtbl.com/i/2024/02/17/65d09ae87b722.png" alt="IMG_4295.PNG" loading="lazy"><br>
3、往下滑找到<strong>Apple Store &amp; iTues USA</strong>并打开<br>
<img src="https://krseoul.imgtbl.com/i/2024/02/17/65d09aef19d07.png" alt="IMG_4296.PNG" loading="lazy"><br>
4、<strong>输入</strong>你要购买的金额($2-$50)<br>
<img src="https://krseoul.imgtbl.com/i/2024/02/17/65d09ae80850d.jpg" alt="IMG_4302.jpg" loading="lazy"><br>
5、点击<strong>立即购买</strong><br>
<img src="https://krseoul.imgtbl.com/i/2024/02/17/65d09ae9166f0.jpg" alt="IMG_4303.jpg" loading="lazy"></p>
<blockquote>
<p>如果你没有注册邮箱并登录，需要进行注册（姓名、邮箱、密码）<br>
<img src="https://ir.imgs.love/2024/02/0/65d0a3dbe6c25.png" alt="搜狗截图20240217201653.png" loading="lazy"><br>
⚠️邮箱一定不要填错，是接收兑换码的重要途径。</p>
</blockquote>
<p>6、选择支付宝支付<br>
<img src="https://krseoul.imgtbl.com/i/2024/02/17/65d09ae5c5099.png" alt="IMG_4304.PNG" loading="lazy"><br>
7、点击<strong>确认支付</strong><br>
<img src="https://krseoul.imgtbl.com/i/2024/02/17/65d09ae75ace2.jpg" alt="IMG_4305.jpg" loading="lazy"><br>
8、确认付款后，点击<strong>完成</strong>，就会跳转到 Pockyt Shop 订单页，支付宝中就可以直接看到礼品卡了，点击<strong>复制</strong>即可。同时，之前注册时填写的邮箱也会收到礼品卡的邮件<br>
⚠️请一定要牢记礼品卡号！不要告诉别人！<br>
<img src="https://i.miji.bid/2024/02/20/ca48a0c724255550403d467e8fb68264.jpeg" alt="ca48a0c724255550403d467e8fb68264.jpeg" loading="lazy"></p>
<h2 id="二-apple-store兑换教程">二、Apple Store兑换教程</h2>
<p>9、打开<strong>Apple Store</strong>并点击右上角<strong>头像</strong><br>
⚠️如果登录的不是需的美区 Apple ID，请退出重新登录<br>
<img src="https://krseoul.imgtbl.com/i/2024/02/17/65d09af05af2e.png" alt="IMG_4307.PNG" loading="lazy"><br>
10、点击<strong>兑换充值卡或代码</strong><br>
<img src="https://krseoul.imgtbl.com/i/2024/02/17/65d09aeb0b11b.jpg" alt="IMG_4308.jpg" loading="lazy"><br>
11、点击<strong>手动输入兑换码</strong><br>
<img src="https://krseoul.imgtbl.com/i/2024/02/17/65d09aeb400d4.png" alt="IMG_4309.PNG" loading="lazy"><br>
12、输入<strong>代码</strong>并点击<strong>兑换</strong>即可<br>
<img src="https://krseoul.imgtbl.com/i/2024/02/17/65d09aed7548e.png" alt="IMG_4310.PNG" loading="lazy"><br>
##三、总结<br>
目前来说，用支付宝美区 Apple ID 礼品卡是操作简单、无需国外银行卡的方法了，不用担心封号，而且没有中间商赚差价，整体的体验非常好</p>
]]></content>
    </entry>
